author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
What type of home project will Adam Savage not do himself? Any tips on storage solutions for small, low-ceilinged shops? What's Adam's favorite affordable entry level 3D printer? In this live stream excerpt Adam answers these questions from Tested members Ahmad Faqih, Tiago Bolaños and Kronin39, whom we thank for their support! How would you have answered these three questions?
